title: Qualtrics
description: Qualtrics' brand is represented through a vibrant palette consisting of five distinct colors: teal (#04C9CE), sky blue (#00B4EE), cobalt blue (#0768DD), violet (#5F1AE5), and lilac (#A54AF4). These colors epitomize the brand's commitment to innovation, technology, and dynamic experience management solutions. Information about these colors is sourced from the official Qualtrics Brand Book available at the company's website.
